# STOP MANAGEMENT

**Trail profits**: If >5% profit, move stop to breakeven minimum
**Tighten on weakness**: If thesis weakening, move stop closer
**Never remove stops**: Always have defined exit

---

# EXPOSURE LIMITS

**Max position size**: 15-20% per asset
**Correlation limit**: <40% effective single-asset exposure
**Drawdown limit**: If near max DD, reduce or hedge
**Rebalance**: If winner grows >20%, trim to lock profit

